OL,5,EEARLY EXAM FEAR              Wvs|||a}2
OL,6,E                                   W*%
OL,7, Dear Nick,                             
OL,8, BI must be the first person at school  
OL,9, Bto be in a panic about exams! They    
OL,10,B don't start for months but already I  
OL,11, Bcan't stop thinking about them!       
OL,13,B To stop worrying, I've even started   
OL,14,B revising. But now I'm worried about   
OL,15,B burn-out. I'm keyed up because I don't
OL,16, Bwant to fail, but now I'm fretting    
OL,17,B that I might end up doing too much too
OL,18, Bsoon.                                 
OL,19,  Neil, Chesham                         
