OL,5,EEARLY EXAM FEAR              Wvs|||a}2
OL,6,E                                   W*%
OL,7, Nick replies,                          
OL,8, BYou can worry too much about exams and
OL,9, Bbuild yourself up into a lather.      
OL,11,B The worst thing abour exams is that   
OL,12, Bnobody ever really teaches you how to 
OL,13,B do them. Why not talk to a teacher    
OL,14,B about your fear?                      
OL,16, BHaving reassurance you've done the    
OL,17, Bright preparation can give confidence.
OL,18, BLook atCHow To Pass Any Exam by Brian 
OL,19,C Duncalf (#6.99) Kyle Cathie.          
